  "text": [
    {
      "startMs": 0,
      "endMs": 0,
      "text": "",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 0.544802889317318,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 0,
      "endMs": 9150,
      "text": "在东京涩谷的深夜实验室里，Claw家族的第三代AI代理正调试着神经接口，而隔壁硅谷的同类系统却因过度依赖云端推理频繁断连；",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 9150,
      "endMs": 9150,
      "text": "",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 0.6493952819475559,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 9150,
      "endMs": 16500,
      "text": "上海张江的Claw轻量版用本地化小模型完成实时方言翻译，旧金山团队则还在为多语言微调耗费数周算力；",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 0.648638025071973,
          "to": 1.25,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1.25,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 300,
          "endMs": 500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 16500,
      "endMs": 16500,
      "text": "",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1,
          "to": 1.25,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1.25,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 300,
          "endMs": 500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 16500,
      "endMs": 24150,
      "text": "柏林工程师发现Claw的自主工具调用链能动态切换API供应商，而竞品仍硬编码三家服务商导致故障率飙升；",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 0.6842167497162596,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 24150,
      "endMs": 24150,
      "text": "",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 0.6966460357626182,
          "to": 1.25,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1.25,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 300,
          "endMs": 500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 24150,
      "endMs": 30900,
      "text": "当孟买贫民窟诊所用Claw离线医疗助手诊断疟疾时，某国际平台因数据合规审查停摆七十二小时；",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 30900,
      "endMs": 30900,
      "text": "",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 0.6160926112164664,
          "to": 1.25,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1.25,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 300,
          "endMs": 500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 30900,
      "endMs": 37200,
      "text": "首尔高中生用Claw教育代理自动生成韩英双语习题，其知识蒸馏机制比传统RAG快四倍；",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 37200,
      "endMs": 37200,
      "text": "",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1,
          "to": 1.25,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1.25,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 300,
          "endMs": 500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 37200,
      "endMs": 45000,
      "text": "但最震撼的是肯尼亚农民手持Claw农业Agent，在无网环境下通过边缘计算识别病虫害并推送本地防治方案；",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 0.5260223229665115,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 45000,
      "endMs": 45000,
      "text": "",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 0.5537747265429924,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 45000,
      "endMs": 54150,
      "text": "这并非技术参数的罗列，而是生态韧性的无声宣言——当别人在修服务器集群的围城，Claw家族早已把根系扎进每寸未被照亮的土壤；",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 0.6097648026722349,
          "to": 1.25,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1.25,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 300,
          "endMs": 500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 54150,
      "endMs": 54150,
      "text": "",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1,
          "to": 1.25,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1.25,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 300,
          "endMs": 500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "startMs": 54150,
      "endMs": 59400,
      "text": "它们不争算力峰值，只问谁真正抵达了用户指尖与呼吸之间那0.3秒的间隙。",
      "position": "center",
      "animations": [
        {
          "type": "scale",
          "from": 1,
          "to": 1,
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 300
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
